Dear Governor,
Thank you for your response and support on this issue!  With all of our legislators from County Commissioners to our Senators in Washington carrying the message that the citizens in Northeast NC oppose any OLF in this area, I would hope we could stop the Navy's consideration for any sites in this area without further delay and impact to our struggling economy.
